summary 'Definer puppet module'
description 'The purpose of this module is to declare resources using hiera. This follows
the philosophy that Puppet should be data driven as much as possible. In
combination with the roles module this pushes as much as possible into the
realm of hiera.'
project_page 'https://github.com/Adaptavist/puppet-definer'

